snippet.title: Aragami 2 - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
From darkness, the Shadow clan has returned. Aragami 2 is coming to Steam, PS4, PS5, Xbox One and Xbox Series X in 2021. 

More info: https://linceworks.com/
